root.title: Casino Joke
root.content: Did you hear the story about the middle aged lady who went to the casino? Sandy went to the casino for the first time and ended up by a table playing roulette. ”How does one decide which number to pick?” She wondered aloud. ”I picked my age” suggested an older gentleman on her left. So Sandy decided to pick the number thirty two. The Croupier gave the wheel a spin, it landed on forty seven, and Sandy fell over in a faint.
